			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original">
					<p>The original transcription is not available.</p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation">
					<p>From: Minister <persName ref="#ehri_dr_masutani">Hideo Masutani</persName> (<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/658225/helsinki.html">Helsinki</placeName>)</p>
					<p>To: MOFA <persName ref="#ehri_dr_shigenori_togo">Togo Shigenori</persName> (<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/1850147/tokyo.html">Tokyo</placeName>)</p>
					<p>Re: Conversation with <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3057568/slovak-republic.html">Slovakian</placeName> Minister about domestic affairs</p>
					<p>….</p>
					<p> 3. The issue of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> who have great influence in <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-816" type="subject">economy</term> is an important <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-351?dlid=deu" type="subject">political issue</term>. Current cabinet minister and head of the <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-397">Hlinka Guard</orgName>
						<persName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000261">Sano Mach</persName> is using his skills to resolve it. </p>
				</div>
			</div>
